    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i hear you. i guess i'm wondering about the \"well-intentioned\" part though. i asked a couple of people at the school board meeting and they basically said that anyone who's worried about it is just being \"intolerant\" or \"outdated.\" is that a fair way to look at it, or are those parents actually missing something important?",
